Company Overview of Davis Selected Advisers LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Davis Selected Advisers LP is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to individuals, high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe with a focus on the United States. It invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations with a focus on large-cap companies. T...
Davis Selected Advisers LP is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to individuals, high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe with a focus on the United States. It invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations with a focus on large-cap companies. The firm employs fundamental and quantitative analysis with a focus on bottom-up and top-down approach to make its investments. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the S&P 500 Index, Russell 3000 Index, MSCI ACWI Index, and MSCI ACWI-ex US Index. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. Davis Selected Advisers LP was founded in 1969 and is based in Tucson, Arizona.
