Davis Institutional

Independent,
Employee-Owned Investment Manager Since 1969Davis Advisors is an independent investment management firm
founded in 1969, serving institutional and individual investors worldwide. Our independence allows us to make what
we believe are the best long-term investment decisions for our clients. Throughout our long history we have
invested successfully through a wide variety of market and economic conditions.1
Focused,
Research-Driven Organization
We focus solely on
investment strategies in which we believe we can add value for investors. All portfolios are managed according to
a single investment discipline of buying durable businesses at value prices and
holding them for the long term.
Long-Term,
High-Conviction Investment Approach
With a long-term
perspective, we devote significant time and resources upfront to studying businesses
rigorously – sometimes over the course of several years – until we build enough
conviction to invest our clients' and our own capital.
Exceptional
Alignment of Interests
The Davis family, Davis
Advisors, employees and directors have more than $2 billion of their own money
invested side by side with clients.2


1Past performance is not a
guarantee of future results. Investment markets are volatile and an investor
may lose money. 2As of December 31, 2016.













